On October 2nd the Mayor of Milan Giuseppe Sala met with management for both Inter Milan and A.C Milan in order to discuss the future of San Siro.<br />
<br />
Giuseppe Sala advised the media &ldquo;We&rsquo;re open to discuss all the available options to our disposal.  The objective is that within the next few months we can come to some a solution for the better of the clubs and for the respective fan bases.  We even discussed a potential new stadium that will be modernized to the value of Milan for the clubs, both teams have very much advised on their interest to invest on the project&rdquo;
